.......... on ..........for the purpose of ..........and that<lb/>
it is requested that a pass may be issued and await him at the<lb/>
Assistant-Provost-Marshal's office at ............</p>

<p><unclear><hi rend="underline">questionable readingOffice Memorandum No.812</hi></unclear><lb/></p>
<opener><dateline><date><unclear>7</unclear>th September, 1915.</date></dateline>
        
    

    
         
